### Request Password Reset
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com"
}

###

### Get Profile (requires Firebase ID token)
# First, login via frontend to get the token, then replace below
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Update Profile (requires token)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Updated Name"
}

###

### Upload Document (requires token)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/documents/upload
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversionMode"

auto
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/sample.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary--

###

### Get User Documents (requires token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents?limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Document by ID (requires token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents/DOCUMENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Conversion History (requires token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents/history?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Pending Documents (Committee/Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents/committee/pending?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer COMMITTEE_OR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Review Document (Committee/Admin only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/documents/DOCUMENT_ID_HERE/review
Authorization: Bearer COMMITTEE_OR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewStatus": "approved",
  "comments": "Document looks good"
}

###

### Delete Document (requires token)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/documents/DOCUMENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get All Documents (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents/admin/all?limit=50&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get User by ID (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/users/USER_UID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Set User Role (Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/auth/users/USER_UID_HERE/role
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "committee"
}

###

### Delete User (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/auth/users/USER_UID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###
